    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try something for the nausea. but honestly i'm just kind of scared to call the doctor because they might tell me to stop taking it or something, and i really need it to stay stable. do you think i could just take an extra dose of my lithium tonight to see if it helps level things out? i feel like if i get a bit more in my system it might stop the weirdness better?",
